predictions.article: Rollins Promises Grain Farmers Improving Ag Economy is a Top Priority
predictions.prediction: The USDA's release of funds for the Environmental Quality Incentive Program and other conservation programs will lead to a 10% increase in applications for these programs by the end of March 2025.

predictions.article: Trade war escalates as retaliatory tariffs hit struggling farm economy
